# EasyDoctor Conventions

## Stack
- Rails 8.1 / Ruby 3.4.5 / PostgreSQL / Hotwire (Turbo + Stimulus) / TailwindCSS

## Templates
- **Always Slim** (`.html.slim`) — never ERB, never HAML
- Forms via `AppFormBuilder` with component-based inputs (`Form::Input::*`)

## Key Gems & Patterns
- **Pagination**: Pagy — never Kaminari or will_paginate
- **Search**: Ransack + ransack-enum
- **Auth**: Devise (invitable, confirmable, 2FA) + SPID via JWT
- **Authorization**: Action Policy (`app/policies/`) — always call `authorize!`
- **Services**: inherit `ApplicationService` (Dry::Initializer), invoke with `ServiceClass.call(**)`
- **Components**: inherit `ApplicationComponent` (Dry::Initializer + ViewComponent)
- **Cloning**: Clowne gem
- **Background jobs**: Solid Queue (database-backed)

## Locale & Time
- Default locale: `it`, available: `en` — always use `t()`, never hardcode Italian strings
- Timezone: `Europe/Rome`
- After editing YAML under `config/locales/`, run `bundle exec i18n-tasks normalize` so CI (`spec/i18n_spec.rb`) stays green

## Frontend JS
- Importmap (no bundler) — Stimulus controllers in `app/javascript/controllers/`

## Deployment
- Kamal with Docker, registry at ghcr.io
- Multi-instance: `easydoctor` and `monzino`
